      <bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545">
         <head altrender="biography" id="a2">BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE </head>
         <p>American missionary in Hangchow, China.</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Pamphlets, brochures, and other materials relating to Hangchow

		  Christian College and other colleges and universities in China, including a

		  typescript history of the college by Mattox, 1952; Presbyterian missions in

		  Hainan and Yunan; religious education in general; and other topics relating to

		  China.</p>
      </scopecontent>
